<div id="review_2768874357" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2768874357" />
    <a title="Loretta" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/18967405-loretta"><img alt="Loretta" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1643728040p2/18967405.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2768874357?book_show_action=true">Apr 15, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Loretta" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Loretta" href="/user/show/18967405-loretta">Loretta</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140184969" href="/book/show/1044996.The_Heart_of_the_Matter">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=classic">classic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=my-2019-reading-challenge">my-2019-reading-challenge</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2768874357" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13833860359573157783">While <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2533.Graham_Greene' title='Graham Greene' rel='nofollow noopener'>Graham Greene</a> tends to be a little wordy for me, I did enjoy this book much more than <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3698.The_Quiet_American' title='The Quiet American by Graham Greene' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Quiet American</a>. I was slightly disappointed though that when the story began speaking of suicide, I knew immediately how the book would end. Four stars.</span>
  <span id="freeText13833860359573157783" style="display:none">While <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2533.Graham_Greene" title="Graham Greene" rel="nofollow noopener">Graham Greene</a> tends to be a little wordy for me, I did enjoy this book much more than <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3698.The_Quiet_American" title="The Quiet American by Graham Greene" rel="nofollow noopener">The Quiet American</a>. I was slightly disappointed though that when the story began speaking of suicide, I knew immediately how the book would end. Four stars.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13833860359573157783" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

