          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/440436-j-c?shelf=i-dont-know-why-i-finished">i-dont-know-why-i-finished</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/440436-j-c?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
